WEBVTT

1
00:52:21.200 --> 00:52:23.220 
每次姐姐赢了我
Every time my sister prevailed...

2
00:52:23.680 --> 00:52:26.700 
父亲就会把我身体的一部分改造成机械
my father would replace a piece of me with machinery...

3
00:52:27.160 --> 00:52:30.180 
说是为了让我像她一样强大
claiming he wanted me to be her equal.

4
00:52:31.200 --> 00:52:33.190 
但她每次都赢
But she won.

5
00:52:33.190 --> 00:52:36.210 
一次 一次又一次
Again and again and again,

6
00:52:36.210 --> 00:52:38.170 
从来没有饶过我一次
never once refraining.

7
00:52:39.230 --> 00:52:43.210 
所以杀了我姐姐之后 我会买一艘
So, after I murder my sister... I will buy a warship

8
00:52:43.210 --> 00:52:45.660 
载满毁灭武器的战舰
with every conceivable instrument of death.

9
00:52:45.690 --> 00:52:49.160 
我会循着我父亲的气息将他慢慢地撕碎
I will hunt my father like a dog and I will tear him apart slowly...

10
00:52:49.210 --> 00:52:51.180 
一片一片的撕碎
piece by piece,

11
00:52:51.180 --> 00:52:55.190 
直到他哪怕体会到我每天都要忍受的
until he knows some semblance of the profound and unceasing pain...

